data.title: I'm Not Single (2008)
data.meta_description: I'm Not Single: Directed by Mohd Pierre Andre. With Farid Kamil, Lisa Surihani, Awal Ashari, Intan Ladyana. I'm Not Single is a story about Maya and Adam couples who are forced to marry at a young age because it was planning of their parents because they were good friends since childhood. Although hate each other and did not have a sense of love, Adam and virtual no reason to object to the design furthermore strongly supported by Maya ancestors were very eager to see the wedding lone granddaughter before his last breath. Maya themselves have a boyfriend that is Dani. Dani and Maya really love each other love and planned to marry. Dani such can not accept the fact Maya married Maya find a way to get back.
